OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776334010
OL,3,CNottingham attack families 'let down'
OL,4,Cby police watchdog
OL,6,FThe top police watchdog boss has said
OL,7,Fthe speed of its investigations has
OL,8,Fadded to the suffering of the families
OL,9,Fof the three people stabbed to death
OL,10,Fby paranoid schizophrenic Valdo
OL,11,FCalocane.
OL,13,FFormer student Calocane fatally
OL,14,Fstabbed 19-year-old undergraduates
OL,15,FBarnaby Webber and Grace O'Malley-
OL,16,FKumar, who were walking home from a
OL,17,Fnight out, in Ilkeston Road,
OL,18,FNottingham, in the early hours of June
OL,19,F13 2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776334010
OL,3,CNottingham attack families 'let down'
OL,4,Cby police watchdog
OL,6,FHe went on to kill grandfather Ian
OL,7,FCoates, 65, in the Mapperley Park area
OL,8,Faround an hour later, stealing his van
OL,9,Fand using it to run over pedestrians
OL,10,Fat two locations in Nottingham city
OL,11,Fcentre.
OL,13,FRachel Watson, the director general of
OL,14,Fthe Independent Office for Police
OL,15,FConduct (IOPC), told the public
OL,16,Finquiry into the attacks that it had
OL,17,F"let down" the families by being "too
OL,18,Fslow" to probe officers' actions.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@JO]yD@bOUzD@EO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776334010
OL,3,CNottingham attack families 'let down'
OL,4,Cby police watchdog
OL,6,FThe IOPC boss told chairwoman Deborah
OL,7,FTaylor she hopes that the ongoing
OL,8,Finvestigations into police actions
OL,9,Fwill be concluded by the time that the
OL,10,FNottingham Inquiry has finished.
OL,12,FMs Watson told the inquiry, which is
OL,13,Fbeing held in central London, on
OL,14,FWednesday: "I wish they (the
OL,15,Finvestigations) had happened and taken
OL,16,Fplace a lot more quickly.
OL,18,F"They have been too slow."
OL,26,@vD@LOUzD@AOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776334010
OL,3,CNottingham attack families 'let down'
OL,4,Cby police watchdog
OL,6,FShe added: "There are some reasons
OL,7,Fbehind this, but that isn't to excuse
OL,8,Fthe length of time which must have
OL,9,Fbeen inordinately painful to the
OL,10,Ffamilies and I'm sure added to their
OL,11,Fsuffering, which the IOPC should not
OL,12,Fbe doing."
OL,14,FShe said the scope of one of the IOPC
OL,15,Finvestigations, which looked into
OL,16,Fpolice contact with Calocane before
OL,17,FJune 13, was drafted "too broadly" and
OL,18,Fwas not of "sufficient quality", which
OL,19,Fcaused a delay.
OL,26,@nD@LOUtD@JO]yD@VOUyD@bO]zD@LOUzD@_O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776334010
OL,3,CNottingham attack families 'let down'
OL,4,Cby police watchdog
OL,6,FMs Watson added: "I should say now,
OL,7,Fthe families did not receive the
OL,8,Fservice they deserve from the IOPC. I
OL,9,Fhave been very clear about that from
OL,10,Fthe outset. And this is one of the
OL,11,Fexamples where the IOPC clearly let
OL,12,Fthem down."
OL,14,FThe inquiry heard that an
OL,15,Finvestigation into complaints against
OL,16,Fformer Nottinghamshire Police chief
OL,17,Fconstable Kate Meynell, relating to
OL,18,Fthe police probe and her communication
OL,19,Fwith the families, has not concluded
OL,20,Fbecause the IOPC is waiting to receive
OL,21,Fa statement from her.
OL,26,@nD@ROUtD@KO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776334010
OL,3,CNottingham attack families 'let down'
OL,4,Cby police watchdog
OL,6,FDuring her evidence to the inquiry
OL,7,Flast month, Ms Meynell, who retired
OL,8,Fafter being diagnosed with cancer last
OL,9,Fyear, apologised for the fact that
OL,10,FCalocane was not arrested by the force
OL,11,Fwhen a warrant was issued for his
OL,12,Farrest months before the attacks.
OL,14,FMs Watson said it is her "deep regret"
OL,15,Fthat families had to press for another
OL,16,FIOPC investigation to be reopened,
OL,17,Fwhich related to the conduct of two
OL,18,FLeicestershire Police officers who
OL,19,Ffailed to arrest Calocane when he
OL,20,Fassaulted two people at a factory
OL,21,Fweeks before the killings.
OL,26,@vD@ZOUvD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776334010
OL,3,CNottingham attack families 'let down'
OL,4,Cby police watchdog
OL,6,FDuring the first investigation into
OL,7,Fthese two officers, Ms Watson said the
OL,8,FIOPC investigator made comments to
OL,9,Fthem during their interview that "came
OL,10,Facross as too friendly and came across
OL,11,Fas almost apologetic".
OL,13,FShe added: "The families were
OL,14,Fconcerned that that did not give them
OL,15,Fassurance that the police were being
OL,16,Fheld to account in a really fair and
OL,17,Fimpartial way."
OL,26,@qD@bOUsD@UO]uD@LOUyD@OO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776334010
OL,3,CNottingham attack families 'let down'
OL,4,Cby police watchdog
OL,6,FThe director general said the IOPC is
OL,7,Ffollowing "new lines" about how
OL,8,FNottinghamshire Police handled
OL,9,Fofficers sharing messages about the
OL,10,Fattacks on WhatsApp, which included
OL,11,Fone message sent by an officer
OL,12,Fdescribing the teenage victims as
OL,13,F"properly butchered".
OL,15,FMs Watson said: "We've also seen
OL,16,Fissues come up during the course of
OL,17,Fthe inquiry that we need to fully
OL,18,Festablish, particularly around how the
OL,19,FWhatsApp group was dealt with, for
OL,20,Fexample.
OL,26,@oD@KOUoD@UO]uD@AOUuD@TO]wD@QOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776334010
OL,3,CNottingham attack families 'let down'
OL,4,Cby police watchdog
OL,6,F"It seems some assurances we had
OL,7,Fthought we had from the force seem to
OL,8,Fhave been called into question, so
OL,9,Fwe've written to the force urgently to
OL,10,Fseek clarity on exactly what audits,
OL,11,Ffor example, that they undertook."
OL,13,FCalocane, who admitted manslaughter
OL,14,Fand attempted murder, is detained
OL,15,Findefinitely in a high-security
OL,16,Fhospital after prosecutors accepted
OL,17,Fhis not guilty pleas to murder on the
OL,18,Fgrounds of diminished responsibility
OL,19,Fin January 2024.
OL,21,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@bO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
